# Create PR Skill

Follow the guidelines in `.ai/skills/create-pr.md` to create a pull request.

## Critical Rules

1. **Always create a new branch for new PRs** - Never reuse existing branches
2. **Always create new branches from up-to-date main**:
   ```bash
   git checkout main
   git pull origin main
   git checkout -b feat/your-feature-name
   ```

## Quick Steps

1. Create branch from main: `git checkout main && git pull && git checkout -b feat/name`
2. Make changes
3. Format: `./gradlew spotlessApply`
4. Test: `./gradlew test && ./gradlew runGametestServer`
5. Build: `./gradlew clean build`
6. Commit: `git commit -m "feat: description"`
7. Push: `git push -u origin feat/name`
8. Create PR: `gh pr create --base main --title "feat: description"`

See `.ai/skills/create-pr.md` for full details.
